high_descs: Walk forward then turn right to face the coffee maker
Pick up the coffee mug from the coffee maker
Turn right and walk up to the fridge
Put the mug in the fridge then remove it
Turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink
Put the mug in the right side of the kitchen sink

Grab the cup in the coffee machine
Turn right, walk to the refrigerator,
open the refrigerator, put the cup in, wait a while, open the refrigerator, take the cup out, close the refrigerator
Turn around, walk to the sink
put the cup in the sink

Grab that mug that is in the coffee maker

Open the fridge and place the mug on the top rack. Close the fridge. Open the fridge and take the mug out. Close the fridge.

Place the mug in the right sink
